I am planning on making this but I just wanted to put in a note about the roux. As many reviewers have figured out, the proportions of butter to flour for the roux are wrong. I went to the web-site for Mr. B's and it contains this same recipe. The roux ingredients, according to Mr. B's, should be 2 cups butter and 2 cups flour.

